<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٢٥٧ -<span class="c5"> حدَّثنا عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ يُوسُفَ:</span> أخبَرَنا مَالِكٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ دِينَارٍ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">عَنْ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ عُمَرَ <span class="special">﵄</span>:</span> أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قالَ: <span class="c2">«إِذَا سَلَّمَ عَلَيْكُمُ الْيَهُودُ، فَإِنَّمَا يَقُولُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗٣٥٠⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">أَحَدُهُمُ:</span> السَّامُ عَلَيْكَ،<span class="c5"> فَقُلْ:</span> وَعَلَيْكَ».<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>